di/" rel="tag">Ivan Iverardi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/julian-kovatchev/" rel="tag">Julian Kovatchev</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/lorenzo-decaro-it/" rel="tag">Lorenzo Decaro @it</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/lucrecia-garcia/" rel="tag">lucrecia garcia</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/nabucco/" rel="tag">Nabucco</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/rossana-rinaldi/" rel="tag">Rossana Rinaldi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/vitalij-kowaljow/" rel="tag">Vitalij Kowaljow</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Abramo Rosalen, Arena di Verona, Cristiano Olivieri, Festival del Centenario 2013, Francesca Micarelli, Gianfranco De Bosio, Ivan Iverardi, Julian Kovatchev, Lorenzo Decaro @it, lucrecia garcia, Nabucco, Opera lirica, Rossana Rinaldi, Vitalij Kowaljow"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/b41b40d04cc32e3e4f904f051c19deec" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Michele-Curnis-120x150.jpg" width="80" height="100" alt="Michele Curnis" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Michele Curnis"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/michele-curnis/">View all articles by Michele Curnis</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text"